metadata.name: Gazoo To The Moon - ORIGINAL PRINT: IT'S ONLY ONE WAY
metadata.description:
The original print of IT'S ONLY ONE WAY by Gazoo To The Moon. This sketch was the model for an animation of the tag which was released in February 2023 during Gazoo's month long residency with DotConnector.

AIR_DROPT to holders of DotConnector x Andre Oshea ART BASEL TOUR 2022
